==English==
===Verb===
'''to administer'''
#''(transitive)'' to cause to [[take]], either by [[openly]] [[offer]]ing or through [[deceit]]
#:''We '''administered''' the medicine to our dog by mixing it in his food.''
#work in an [[administrative]] capacity; [[supervise]]

